text:
One of the earliest commercial building that houses the earliest Tech, Media and Research organisations comparing from both the Public and Private sectors.
Have quite a handful of food and beverages options and some retails shops located at the same premises.

Big facility with swimming pool and leisure area. 2 studios for classes. Clean changing room with steam room. Friendly staffs. Easy access with MRT station and carpark right below the building. Plenty foodcourts, restaurants and supermarket at the same building.

Modern building with office towers and many F&B outlets located in basement levels.

Directly connected to the subway Metro station.
Office cum retail outlets cater to the office workers.
